The paper discusses the optimization of fuzzy inference systems using neural network learning and evolutionary computation. This topic falls under the broad category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks and evolutionary computation also suggests the sub-categories of neural networks (cs.NE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the optimization of fuzzy inference systems can be applied to various engineering fields, such as control engineering (cs.CE).
